	<div class="postzoom"><h1><a href="2008_11_27_new_blog_engine">New blog engine</a></h1>
<p>I successfully moved this site from a Wordpress blog to <a href="http://github.com/adamwiggins/scanty/">scanty</a>, with some <a href="http://github.com/swenson/scanty/">modifications</a>.</p>

<p>I think I have it nearly all working except my old comments.  Rest assured that I have them all (and they are all stored in Disqus), but I haven't gotten them all linked properly.</p>

<p>Let me know if anything is too broken.</p>
